desc_long								关于这款游戏							Emma was living alone with her younger brother until one day he has disappeared in eerie circumstances. Help Emma find her brother and learn what has happened.GameplayThe Madness of Little Emma is a randomly generated action platformer with heavy Rogue-like elements. In her journey Emma will discover tons of varied items and encounter multitudes of unique enemies.Key Features:Over 100 hours of challenging gameplayOver 250 items5 playable characters - each with completely different playstyleAlmost a hundred unique enemy types25 bossesFive episodes and multiple hidden areasPersistent Steam leaderboard (with monthly resets)A curious story6 cutscenes (intro + 5 endings)XB360 Controller supportTop-quality pixel artCinematic musicLots of Achievements and unlockablesTons of Secrets						
